.com/index.php/2019/05/23/cover-me-buckwheat-zydeco-back-in-your-arms/", "url_meta": {"origin": 14358, "position": 4}, "title": "Cover Me, Buckwheat Zydeco: Back in Your Arms", "author": "Ken", "date": "May 23, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "One of the last songs Buckwheat Zydeco recorded in the studio was a reggae reinvention of Bruce's torch song, \"Back in Your Arms.\" And it works.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/buck.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57873, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/29/kingdom-of-days-july-29-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 14358, "position": 5}, "title": "July 29", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 29, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Happy birthday, Patti Scialfa, born on this date in 1953! Watch Bruce wish his wife a happy birthday by premiering \"Give the Girl a Kiss\" in her honor. More highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/admin-ajax-52.jpg?fit=1200%2C1044&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/admin-ajax-52.jpg?fit=1200%2C1044&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/admin-ajax-52.jpg?fit=1200%2C1044&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/admin-ajax-52.jpg?fit=1200%2C1044&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/admin-ajax-52.jpg?fit=1200%2C10